Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.48,0:01:30.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.52,0:01:32.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不過重要的是接下來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.53,0:01:35.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒錯 這次絕對要進到決賽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.07,0:01:36.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,跟大家一起分享喜悅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.45,0:01:38.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小香音可是卯足了幹勁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.32,0:01:42.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,也有人已經感動到說不出話來就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.83,0:01:43.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.33,0:01:46.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真的非常感謝各位
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.62,0:01:48.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我身為學生會長
