Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.09,0:07:30.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,為什麼妳都只想得到這種把戲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.26,0:07:32.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,堇不也是這個樣子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.97,0:07:34.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,反應好冷淡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.55,0:07:36.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那就採取正攻法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.22,0:07:39.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在網路上散布葳恩．瑪格麗特的謠言
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.64,0:07:41.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,搞個大炎上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.06,0:07:42.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這是哪門子的正攻法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.94,0:07:46.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這在網路世界已經是很正統的正攻法了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.11,0:07:47.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,別說那種亂七八糟的話啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.24,0:07:52.41,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,千砂都學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.41,0:07:54.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,有什麼在意的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.83,0:07:57.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.42,0:08:05.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那就明天見囉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.63,0:08:06.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.42,0:08:07.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,先告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.46,0:08:09.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,路上小心喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.30,0:08:12.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,二年級的可以留下來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.51,0:08:15.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,一年級嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.05,0:08:19.35,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,看過影片後我就清楚了解到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.35,0:08:22.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們之間的實力差距還是很大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.60,0:08:24.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,一年級們已經很努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.52,0:08:26.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,像是上次的舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.19,0:08:28.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,也能跟我們跳相同的舞步了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.73,0:08:30.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這我當然明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.98,0:08:31.90,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.90,0:08:33.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳的意思是跳得出來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.07,0:08:36.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,跟能不能贏是兩回事對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.57,0:08:37.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這樣下去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.74,0:08:40.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們會很難晉級決賽嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.24,0:08:42.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,大概吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.66,0:08:44.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,所以千砂都妳覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.54,0:08:47.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,讓一年級瘋狂特訓會比較好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.75,0:08:49.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我就是想聽聽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.59,0:08:51.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,大家覺得怎麼做比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.22,0:08:53.93,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不過 要是告訴一年級的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.93,0:08:55.18,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,會讓她們很介意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.18,0:08:56.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,當然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.47,0:08:59.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,她們本來就覺得自己跟我們有差距了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.85,0:09:02.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不必告訴她們也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.81,0:09:03.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小可可…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.35,0:09:06.31,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,一年級已經很努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.31,0:09:07.90,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要是現在說出來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.90,0:09:10.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,很可能會讓她們努力過度
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.36,0:09:13.03,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,連唱歌都變得難受
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.03,0:09:14.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但是 妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.20,0:09:16.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,可可希望大家能一起開心唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.70,0:09:19.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我也贊成
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.53,0:09:22.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那麼 這件事就對她們保密
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.99,0:09:26.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,來稍微調整一下練習菜單吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.29,0:09:27.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.42,0:09:32.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那小千跟小可可
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.50,0:09:34.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,練習菜單就麻煩妳們囉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.22,0:09:35.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.80,0:09:37.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那麼就明天再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.36,0:09:58.78,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳為什麼會走這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.78,0:10:00.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳家在另一邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:02.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我還有地方要去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.20,0:10:04.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那妳自己去就好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.29,0:10:06.41,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,可可要回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.96,0:10:08.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.88,0:10:14.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,什麼好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.17,0:10:16.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,如果沒在Love Live拿出成績
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.09,0:10:18.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳就會被帶回上海
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.26,0:10:19.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這件事應該沒變吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.68,0:10:23.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,去年還能逃過一劫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.97,0:10:27.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就表示今年非得拿出成績不可 不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.02,0:10:32.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這件事…跟堇無關
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.27,0:10:34.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,哪裡無關了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.77,0:10:38.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,至少對Liella!來說至關重要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.07,0:10:40.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳就這麼無法信任大家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.20,0:10:43.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,可可!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.20,0:10:45.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我討厭妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.50,0:10:49.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,跟大家說清楚比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.79,0:10:51.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我辦不到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.25,0:10:54.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,可可想跟大家一起開心唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.17,0:10:59.18,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那才是可可夢想中的學園偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.51,0:11:01.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,可可
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.56,0:11:05.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,等等 可可!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.99,0:11:20.86,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(葳恩．瑪格麗特 確定出賽LOVELIVE! 東京大賽!!)\N(上回王者Sunny Passion 於地區大賽惜敗!!)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.45,0:11:29.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,奇怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.54,0:11:30.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,澀谷香音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.84,0:11:37.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳為什麼會在這種地方唱歌?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.05,0:11:42.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我來告訴妳什麼叫真正的歌聲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.05,0:11:46.93,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳所處的舞台是多麼渺小又無趣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.93,0:11:48.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我就讓妳好好見識一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.64,0:11:50.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,一點都不無趣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.39,0:11:52.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們歌唱的舞台…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.64,0:11:55.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Love Live是最棒的場所
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.69,0:11:56.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.57,0:11:58.90,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那就記住我說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.90,0:12:01.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,比賽當天妳就知道意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.79,0:12:17.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,安安
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.59,0:12:22.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,今天開始要更新練習菜單
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.09,0:12:25.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,終於要為東京大賽做準備了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.51,0:12:26.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,幹勁十足呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.89,0:12:29.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我現在就在擔心會不會肌肉痠痛了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.81,0:12:31.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,堇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.98,0:12:35.10,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在這之前我有話想說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.10,0:12:36.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.23,0:12:38.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,下一次舞台…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.07,0:12:43.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我認為只讓二年級五人上台比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.36,0:12:47.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Love Live! Superstar!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.78,0:12:49.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小堇…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.87,0:12:51.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳是認真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.37,0:12:54.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是啊 我昨天想了一整晚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.04,0:12:55.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要贏過那個女生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.46,0:12:58.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,想進到決賽 就只能這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.96,0:13:00.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,堇…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.21,0:13:03.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,為什麼 妳就那麼怕她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.05,0:13:05.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,她打敗了Sunny Passion耶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.01,0:13:06.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這是當然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.09,0:13:08.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,說得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.14,0:13:10.18,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就算這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.18,0:13:12.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們也不一定會輸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.64,0:13:16.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,可是 主辦方會允許只有五人登台嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.02,0:13:17.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.02,0:13:20.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,雖然禁止沒參加預賽的成員上場
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.23,0:13:23.03,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但不得已有人缺席的情況當然沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.65,0:13:25.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,只要我們不上台…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.32,0:13:28.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就能讓學姐們進行更完美的演出
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.74,0:13:30.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,意思是這樣嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.74,0:13:32.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不要說這種蠢話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.29,0:13:33.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.33,0:13:36.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,只有五人上台 就算贏了也沒意義
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.46,0:13:37.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們的目標是和校內的大家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.83,0:13:39.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,一起獲勝 分享喜悅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.92,0:13:40.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.55,0:13:43.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要是輸了該怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.38,0:13:46.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,會有很多人傷心…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.47,0:13:47.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.63,0:13:50.35,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不如選擇更有機會獲勝的方法…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.93,0:13:54.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳們聽見了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.23,0:13:56.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,一年級的也這樣說了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.52,0:13:59.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小堇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.60,0:14:01.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們必須獲勝啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.27,0:14:03.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我也是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.11,0:14:06.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但如果不是Liella!全員上場就沒意義了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.45,0:14:07.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,畢竟…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.74,0:14:10.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,大家都在才是Liella!啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.16,0:14:20.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我啊 可是想回歸演藝圈的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.88,0:14:22.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我必須在這裡拿出成績
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.42,0:14:24.71,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,得到更多更多更多人的矚目
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.71,0:14:27.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,回到那個世界去才行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.84,0:14:31.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,所以我不可以在這種地方輸掉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.47,0:14:34.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳這話是認真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.31,0:14:37.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,回答我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.10,0:14:40.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,當然是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.48,0:14:46.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不要再說了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.03,0:14:49.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小可可…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.86,0:14:52.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,請不要…再說了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.67,0:15:02.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,抱歉拖到這麼晚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.59,0:15:04.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,明天會照預定計畫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.04,0:15:05.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,從早上開始練習
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.80,0:15:08.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真的沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.47,0:15:11.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是的 我們會去談談的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.72,0:15:13.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,各位就跟平常一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.47,0:15:15.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,為下一次舞台做準備吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.89,0:15:21.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,接下來…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.39,0:15:23.35,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,總之就先讓我一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.35,0:15:26.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,聽聽小堇的說法可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.15,0:15:27.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小千…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.90,0:15:30.03,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我明白小香音的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.03,0:15:33.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我想大家應該都支持香音同學的意見
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.70,0:15:37.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不過 小堇她也有自己的考量…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.33,0:15:40.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我剛剛太大聲了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.79,0:15:41.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.75,0:15:43.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我很高興喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.46,0:15:45.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,知道小香音是這麼認真
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.54,0:15:49.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,也真的很在乎所有成員
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.38,0:15:50.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.26,0:15:51.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小戀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.72,0:15:52.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,請問…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.01,0:15:58.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,能不能讓可可去找堇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.35,0:16:03.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.85,0:16:06.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,也只能先照學姐們的指示做了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.52,0:16:09.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,學姐們會說服堇學姐的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.20,0:16:13.78,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳們覺得這樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.53,0:16:15.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,芽衣…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.49,0:16:20.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,學姐是為了我們著想才那麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.41,0:16:25.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但她其實應該跟堇學姐一樣想贏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.09,0:16:29.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,畢竟校內同學們也很期待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.00,0:16:32.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這一年來都是為了這一刻努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.43,0:16:35.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小芽衣是怎麼想的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.39,0:16:38.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,希奈子呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.39,0:16:44.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,振作起來啊 堇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.56,0:16:47.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳不是已經做好扮黑臉的覺悟了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.94,0:16:50.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.40,0:16:51.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.44,0:16:53.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這個我可以拿走嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.65,0:16:55.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.86,0:16:58.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小氣鬼 討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.83,0:17:07.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,討厭 到底要我怎麼辦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.42,0:17:10.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳們…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.84,0:17:14.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,堇學姐 妳那副打扮…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.51,0:17:16.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,很適合耶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.39,0:17:17.93,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.93,0:17:19.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,既然家裡經營神社
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.22,0:17:20.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這點事我還是會做的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.64,0:17:22.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,所以 妳們有什麼事?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.52,0:17:26.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒有 只是想讓堇學姐聽聽而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.60,0:18:09.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,剛剛我們四個已經把心意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.94,0:18:12.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,傳達給堇學姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.02,0:18:14.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,所以我們不會登上下次的舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.73,0:18:18.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,東京大賽就由二年級的五個人參加
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.53,0:18:20.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,然後請讓我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.28,0:18:23.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,看看學姐們獲勝的樣子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.16,0:18:28.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳們幾個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.42,0:18:30.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.88,0:18:34.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能做得出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.55,0:18:38.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳們也不想想自己努力練習了多久
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.05,0:18:39.18,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,從早到晚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.18,0:18:41.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,每天每天都為了Love Live練習
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.93,0:18:43.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.97,0:18:45.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳們是為了跟大家一起分享喜悅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.97,0:18:47.43,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,才努力過來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.43,0:18:51.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,總覺得堇學姐說的話好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.48,0:18:55.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是堇學姐說希望只由二年級五人出場的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.36,0:18:57.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.44,0:18:59.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,九個人一起上台就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.74,0:19:01.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,可可學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.91,0:19:08.71,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,最重要的是大家一起唱歌這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.71,0:19:11.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,大家一起呈現最棒的舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.46,0:19:13.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但是…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.63,0:19:20.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,可可都說沒關係了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.01,0:19:22.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,為什麼妳老是要做些多餘的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.72,0:19:24.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,老是要擅自替我擔心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.51,0:19:27.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我不要啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.27,0:19:31.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我還想跟妳在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.94,0:19:35.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這三年都想跟妳一起當學園偶像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.28,0:19:40.90,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,可可是大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.20,0:19:44.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,堇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.12,0:19:45.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小堇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.25,0:19:52.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,堇…?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.96,0:19:56.88,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.80,0:19:59.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我被這個給拯救了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.51,0:20:02.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,所以我想要回報妳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.34,0:20:03.68,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,希望我的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.68,0:20:06.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,能讓妳當學園偶像直到最後
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.26,0:20:09.93,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我絕對不要讓妳回上海去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.93,0:20:11.35,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,上海…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.35,0:20:13.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.81,0:20:15.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要是沒贏就必須回去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.65,0:20:19.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,如果沒留下成績 她就…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.28,0:20:23.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,可可就會被帶走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.11,0:20:25.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,再也見不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.37,0:20:28.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳真傻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.88,0:20:35.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,可可…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.96,0:20:41.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,堇真的只會做多餘的事耶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.34,0:20:43.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,盡是做些可可討厭的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.22,0:20:47.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,反對可可做的決定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.09,0:20:50.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,只要可可開口就一定會插嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.39,0:20:52.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,少囉嗦…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.32,0:21:03.03,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我真的很討厭妳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.45,0:21:07.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,最討厭妳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.87,0:21:10.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,也最喜歡妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.63,0:21:21.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要怎麼做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.05,0:21:23.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還用問嗎 小千
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.30,0:21:24.68,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.01,0:21:27.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好了 完成囉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.97,0:21:29.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.26,0:21:31.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是為了讓大家都能參加東京大賽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.60,0:21:32.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,所準備的特訓菜單喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.31,0:21:35.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這麼多…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.64,0:21:36.90,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,辦得到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.90,0:21:38.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳這個沒體力的愛哭鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.81,0:21:40.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這句話原封不動還給妳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.11,0:21:41.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳這隻愛哭鬼具足蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.15,0:21:48.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那麼 一年級的做好覺悟了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.28,0:21:50.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,今天就要開始特訓了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.70,0:21:52.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,為了讓我們九個一起獲勝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.21,0:21:58.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Liella!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.04,0:22:02.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Super start!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.97,0:22:13.68,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在我追逐的夢想前方 總是能看見
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.68,0:22:16.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,名為希望的星辰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.89,0:22:21.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,正在閃爍著 閃爍耀眼光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.56,0:22:24.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,即便跌倒也能再次前進
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.19,0:22:29.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在我追逐的夢想前方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.45,0:22:34.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我究竟會走向何處呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.99,0:22:39.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,場場相遇之中 雖然又會迷惘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.96,0:22:43.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,請試著去享受這一切吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.46,0:22:46.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,覺得「似乎能做到卻做不到」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.59,0:22:48.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,最後做到的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.88,0:22:51.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就會很開心 想著要好好加油
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.14,0:22:55.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,整顆心都像是要跳了出來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.35,0:23:00.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,盡情歡笑 放聲高歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.19,0:23:02.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,想傳達給你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.40,0:23:06.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,繼續走向遠方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.28,0:23:08.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,世界廣闊無邊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.11,0:23:11.41,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,雖然也有景色會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.41,0:23:14.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但熱情會始終如一!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.87,0:23:18.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,跨越許多後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.50,0:23:20.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,想實現的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.50,0:23:24.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,來吧 大家一起去實現
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.50,0:23:29.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,明天要彈奏出什麼樣的悸動呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.63,0:23:33.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,去改變未來吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.18,0:23:39.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,下集 響徹澀谷的歌聲
